# Advent of Code 2023

Solutions to the [Advent of Code](https://adventofcode.com/) problems for 2023

 ### Running the tests for a specific day

 * change into the directory for the specific day
 * run the test script

```
$ cd 01
$ ruby aoc_test.rb
```

### Run against the input file

* change into the directory for the specific day
* run the script using `input.txt` as STDIN for the script

```
$ cd 01
$ cat input.txt | ./aoc.rb
```
